Guys let's be honest, this is not as bad as people think. I mean- it's all fresh, delicious meet getting me very excited, and this scene might take place in some fantasy world where cannibalism is actually somewhat common. 

Not sure but if we had to put more detail into this doujin, we'd expect more than just flesh getting cut. I honestly can't describe "detailed" in words, but maybe visualization would do it; in comparison to other doujins, you'd see the difference.

So this doujin is half as bad as people think, and besides that, these girls seem excited and curious as well... they're not really trying to fight against it, so you shouldn't feel ashamed at all! 
They deserve to die anyway, don't you think so!? Ha~! <3
